section.section:
"Civil action" includes:
An appeal of an administrative remedy to any court;
A petition for mandamus against the prisoner's custodian, its officers or employees, or any official or employee of the Department;
Any tort claim against a custodian, the custodian's officers or employees, or any employee or official of the Department;
Any action alleging a violation of civil rights against a custodian, the custodian's officers and employees, or any official or employee of the Department; or
Any appeal, application for leave to appeal, or petition for certiorari.
